%N A394557 G.f. A(x) satisfies [x^n] exp(n^3*x) (1 - E^3(x*A(x))) = 0 for n > 0, where E is the Euler operator x*d/dx.
%F A394557 a(n) = A107675(n)/(n+1)^3.
%F A394557 1/(n+1)! = Sum_{k=0..n} ((k+1)/(n+1)^(k+1))^3 * a(k)/(n-k)!.
